    "A greedy decoding strategy was employed for generation for all the models.",
    "To mitigate repetition issues, we applied a repetition penalty of 1.1 and set the no-repeat n-gram size to 5.",
    "We presented the average results in the main text.",
    "To provide a quantifiable measure of uncertainty in the measurement or prediction and help other researchers replicate our experiments, we also reported the standard deviations with RoBERTa models on the GLUE benchmark in Table 17, and the standard deviations with GPT-2 on the E2E NLG Challenge in Table 18.",
